* [[文治]] 1st year ([[Julian calendar]] [[1185]] [[November 10]]) – Horikawa Night Raid. Under the secret orders of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tosa-bō Masatoki attacked the Horikawa Hall in Kyoto where {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshitsune|ja|義経|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was present, but was repelled.

