{{Not to be confused with|October 17|qq=October 17}}[[Category:Days of the Japanese Lunisolar Calendar]]<!--why is this category always showing up as 347 members?--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月十七|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 17일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 17''' is the 17th day of the month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (Old Calendar)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}}, the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦 (Old Calendar)|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyo|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyo|qq=}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomobiki|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜}}.
== Events == * [[:en:文治|文治]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1185|1185]] [[:en:November 10|November 10]]) – Horikawa Night Raid. Under the secret orders of [[:en:Minamoto no Yoritomo|Minamoto no Yoritomo]], Tosa-bō Masatoki attacked the Horikawa Hall in Kyoto where {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshitsune|ja|義経|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoshitsune|qq=}} was present, but was repelled.
== Births ==
== Deaths == * [[:en:Kōan (Kamakura period)|Kōan]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1280|1280]] [[November 30]]) – Enni, a monk of the Rinzai sect during the mid-Kamakura period (born [[:en:1202|1202]]). * [[:en:Keichō|Keichō]] 7th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1602|1602]] [[November 30]]) – Tachibana Kinchiyo, head of the Tachibana clan (born [[:en:1569|1569]]). * [[:en:Manji (era)|Manji]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1658|1658]] [[November 30]]) – Sanada Nobuyuki, the first lord of the Ueda Domain in Shinano, later the first lord of the Matsushiro Domain in Shinano. * [[:en:享和|享和]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1803|1803]] [[November 30]]) – Maeno Ryōsaku, a Rangaku (Dutch Learning) scholar (born [[:en:1723|1723]]).
