'''October 17''' is the 17th day of the month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (Old Calendar)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|comment=enwiki is a redirect}}, the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦 (Old Calendar)|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyo|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyo|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|WD=Q96759840|1=tomobiki}}{{efn|ja|友引|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}{{efn|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomobiki|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}.

== Events ==
* [[:en:文治|文治]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1185|en|1185|WD=Q19729|lt=1185|1=1185}} {{ill|November 10|en|November 10|WD=Q2988|lt=November 10|1=November 10}}) – Horikawa Night Raid. Under the secret orders of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|en|Minamoto no Yoritomo|WD=Q242800|lt=Minamoto no Yoritomo|1=Minamoto no Yoritomo}}, Tosa-bō Masatoki attacked the Horikawa Hall in Kyoto where {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshitsune|ja|義経|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoshitsune|qq=}} was present, but was repelled.

